### README.md (5 changes)

**Line 195:** borrow_call_to_operator
```
194: | `our<T>` | Shared ownership | Reference counting | `config<our<Settings>> = our(Settings{...})` |
195: | `their<T>` | Borrowed reference | Non-owning access | `ref<their<Data>> = borrow(owner)` |
196: | `loc<T>` | Raw pointer | Unsafe operations only | `ptr<loc<Int>> = loc(variable)` |
```
**Change:** `borrow(owner)` → `borrow owner`

